947
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:21,940
 i šta ja znam

948
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,040
 i koje imaju umjetne sise

949
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:24,580
 i toga sam se nagledao,

950
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:25,060
 bože moj.

951
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:26,480
 Ne ma više ove prave,

952
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:27,800
 draži sam ove naše cure

953
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:28,440
