957
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:32,320
 i šta ja znam,

958
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:34,120
 nego sve te iz Hollywooda.

959
00:40:34,120 --> 00:40:34,700
 Međutim,

960
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:36,140
 jadne te naše hrvatice

961
00:40:36,140 --> 00:40:36,840
 nemaju pojma.

962
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:37,160
 Mislim,

963
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:38,960
 one primaju te krive modela izvana.

964
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,660
 A oni ne znaju koliko su te babe,

965
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:41,340
 da budem prost,

966
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:42,820
 nesretne u Americi.

967
00:40:43,580 --> 00:40:45,280
 sto posto brakova u Americi

968
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:45,660
 završio,

969
00:40:45,660 --> 00:40:47,020
 70 posto rastova,

970
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:47,560
 razumijete.

971
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:49,300
 Kaj mi je onda to onda?

972
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:49,500
 Zna,

973
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:51,460
 tam se zaklinja tu neku veliku ljubav

974
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:52,460
 i onda nakon dve,

975
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:52,940
 tri godine

976
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:54,160
 svaki ide na svoju stranu.

977
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:55,100
 To meni nije,

978
00:40:55,100 --> 00:40:55,960
 to nije sudbina,

979
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:56,380
 to nije,

980
00:40:56,380 --> 00:40:57,500
 šta smo,

981
00:40:57,500 --> 00:40:58,320
 ne sad smo skrenuli malo te.

982
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,900
 Rekli ste da volite ljepotu

983
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,900
 i da padate u depresiju.

984
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:02,100
 Da, pa volim da imam mir,

985
00:41:02,100 --> 00:41:02,680
 a ve, pa jeste,

986
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:03,540
 što me smete?

987
00:41:03,540 --> 00:41:03,760
 I da padate u depresiju,

988
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,720
 zbog čega najviše?

989
00:41:04,720 --> 00:41:05,780
 Kao prvajca,

990
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:07,380
 to malo subjektivno zvuči

991
00:41:07,380 --> 00:41:07,940
 i tak dalje.

992
00:41:07,940 --> 00:41:09,480
 Sad više što sam ja nekad

993
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,640
 isto bio hippie i tako.

994
00:41:10,640 --> 00:41:12,520
 Ne volim ljude,

995
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:14,360
 ne volim kad idem po gradu,

996
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,240
 no vidim ljude da se tetoviraju

997
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:17,440
 od glave do nogu

998
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,480
 i čak ljudi ozbiljnije.

999
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,360
 To mi, mislim,

1000
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,460
 to mi kao da mi je neki feler,

1001
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:21,620
 kao da mi je gubitak

1002
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:22,580
 nekog identiteta.

1003
00:41:22,580 --> 00:41:23,860
 Drugo, ne volim to,

1004
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:25,340
 to je čisto zvučno,

1005
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:25,860
