1006
00:41:25,860 --> 00:41:27,740
 Kad danas vi ne možete praktički

1007
00:41:27,740 --> 00:41:27,980
 otići,

1008
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:29,300
 tipični amerikanizam.

1009
00:41:29,300 --> 00:41:31,000
 To je meni prvo šokiralo

1010
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:31,580
 u Americi.

1011
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:32,600
 idete u baru,

1012
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,300
 idete na WC,

1013
00:41:33,300 --> 00:41:34,080
 idete bilo gdje.

1014
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,200
 Uvijek imate neku

1015
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:36,240
 pregušujuću muziku

