00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:36,960
 u kojoj dolazi.

1017
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,760
 Pa ja sam samostalan čovjek,

1018
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:39,800
 nisam autista,

1019
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:40,900
 ali volim biti,

1020
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:42,000
 pusti da stvaram

1021
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:42,880
 svoj sam svijet,

1022
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,260
 ne da mi tuli kad idem,

1023
00:41:44,260 --> 00:41:45,780
 neću sada govoriti

1024
00:41:45,780 --> 00:41:46,800
 koja firma ili koja,

1025
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:47,200
 kad ideš.

1026
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:47,700
 Nije bitno,

1027
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:48,680
 želite mir svoj tišir.

1028
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:49,280
 Očeo mir,

1029
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,920
 stavno mi trubi neka glazba,

1030
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,020
 stavno trubi ovo,

1031
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:53,040
 stavno ovo,

1032
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:54,060
 to je jedna stvar.

1033
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:55,100
 A druga stvar,

1034
00:41:55,100 --> 00:41:56,080
 cijeli taj sistem

1035
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,340
 se poremetio zašto?

1036
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,420
 A tu je glavna tema,

1037
00:41:58,420 --> 00:41:59,220
 je liberalizam.

1038
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:00,740
 Ja nisam samo kritičan

1039
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:01,560
 prema komunizmu.

1040
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:02,720
 Liberalizam je on

1041
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:04,460
 jako perfidan sistem

1042
00:42:04,460 --> 00:42:05,360
 kojeg se sad diže

1043
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:06,380
 do nebesa,

1044
00:42:06,380 --> 00:42:07,840
 ali koji u biti

1045
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,800
 razara na jedan

1046
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:09,840
 vrlo podmuklel,

1047
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,120
 vrlo elegantan način

1048
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:12,300
 nacionalno svijesti

1049
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:15,380
 i kulturno svijest

1050
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:16,160
 i sve kod nas.

1051
00:42:16,160 --> 00:42:16,780
 To vidite,

1052
00:42:16,780 --> 00:42:17,960
 svaki dan to gledate,

1053
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:19,840
 ljudi pomahnite li se za novcem,

1054
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,760
 onda ideologija progresa,

1055
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,180
 jer to je kod komunizma

1056
00:42:23,180 --> 00:42:24,020
 i kapitalizma,

1057
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:25,500
 jedna te ista stvar.

1058
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:26,760
 I jedan i drugi teže

1059
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:27,940
 prema tom jednom sretnom.

1060
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:28,080
 Ali kako je moguće

1061
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:28,680
 da mi koji smo,

1062
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:29,220
 mi,

1063
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:31,640
 ljudi s ovih prostora,

1064
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:32,660
 prošli smo to

1065
00:42:32,660 --> 00:42:33,680
 pranje mozga,

1066
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,400
 ću ja reći,

1067
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,420
 u onoj državi.

1068
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:36,240
 Kako opet sad

1069
00:42:36,240 --> 00:42:37,040
 pristajemo na to

1070
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:37,860
 pranje mozga

1071
00:42:37,860 --> 00:42:38,540
 zapadno,

1072
00:42:38,540 --> 00:42:39,420
 ne znam,

1073
00:42:39,420 --> 00:42:41,020
 moderno,

1074
00:42:41,020 --> 00:42:42,480
 kao napredno,

1075
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:43,580
 a taj zapad

1076
00:42:43,580 --> 00:42:44,620
 s druge strane

1077
00:42:44,620 --> 00:42:45,520
 je definitivno

1078
00:42:45,520 --> 00:42:46,680
 dekadentan i propada?

1079
00:42:46,680 --> 00:42:47,060
 Absolutno,

1080
00:42:47,060 --> 00:42:47,540
 dekadentan,

1081
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:49,160
 ja ne mogu se da reći

1082
00:42:49,160 --> 00:42:49,940
 da će to biti sutra

1083
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:50,500
 ili prekosta.

1084
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:51,680
 Ima zdravih elementa,

1085
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:52,080
 svugdje.

1086
00:42:52,080 --> 00:42:53,220
 I ja srećam,

1087
00:42:53,220 --> 00:42:53,740
 ja sam s njima

1088
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:54,360
 i u kontaktu,

1089
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:54,780
 možemo,

1090
00:42:54,780 --> 00:42:55,960
 ljudi me objavljuju

1091
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:56,340
 i tako da.

1092
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,200
 Ima normalne,

1093
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,460
 ali ljudima isto teško.

